{
  "stem": "2170.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 32.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And as soon as he came back-- I mean, we still got a letter from my father.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in June-- I don't remember exactly the day-- June 18 or 15-- the Germans attacked the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then, [SIGHS] we knew already-- this is it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "As the Germans attacked, the Russians, in the beginning, tried to talk to the people, especially the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was actually a speech by Stalin, or Molotov, that the Jews should be evacuated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But many did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We lived a little bit far from the main station of Zhmerinka.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We didn't have the train close.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my mother was like, she didn't feel like to run no more.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But my older brother-- my older brothers and my brother-in-law was taken in-- into the army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they had to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was left with my sisters and my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we saw a lot of Russian Army running away, and the Jewish people trying, with whoever could, to run.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Germans came in attacking all the time with planes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we just stayed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was our destiny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We cannot go nowhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother wasn't feeling good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brothers was not with us anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what it-- it was around that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And soon, soon the Germans start already to attacking and coming in to my town in Brailov.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the beginning, when they came in--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1941, in, I would say, in September, before the holidays-- before the Jewish holidays in September.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they came in, in the beginning-- it was a small town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not-- yeah, and the Ukrainians, the population-- they already showed who they are.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
